description: Mama Gia is bringing out the best and freshest Italian eats on the Kansas City streets. You’re invited to the corner of Holmes & Blue Ridge where you can find Mama Gia in her trailer, making mouthwatering made-to-order meals. Her menu changes daily but you’ll always find her famous staples; the Grilled Chicken Caesar Wrap, Italian Sausage Sandwich with homemade red sauce, savory sauteed bell peppers & onions, and the ever-tasty Quesadilla Pizza. And if you’re jonesing for a breakfast of eggs & potatoes, Mama Gia has always got you covered. Her specialty beverages (Pineapple Smoothie and Grapefruit Spritzer) are also all the rage. Make your way to Mama Gia’s Streets Eats for the most amazing Italian cuisine.
name: Mama Gia's Street Eats
